    "title": "Filipo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "filipo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Filipo alikuwa miongoni mwa wa kwanza kushiriki Habari Njema kuhusu Yesu na watu nje ya Yudea. Akiwa anaheshimiwa sana na Wakristo wa mwanzo, alikuwa mmoja wa wanaume saba waliochaguliwa kusimamia mpango wa ugawaji wa chakula kwa waumini wenye uhitaji huko Yerusalemu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1-Acts6:6\">Matendo 6:1–6</a>). Filipo alikuwa mhubiri mwenye nguvu na ufanisi (Mhubiri wa Habari Njema) kupitia nguvu za Roho.</p><p>Baada ya kifo cha Stefano, Wakristo walikimbia Yerusalemu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:1-Acts8:5\">Matendo 8:1–5</a>). Filipo alipeleka ujumbe wa Kristo Samaria, mji ulio na watu wa aina mbalimbali. Huko, aliwaponya wengi na kufukuza roho waovu, na watu walipokea kwa hamu ujumbe wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:5-Acts8:8\">Matendo 8:5–8</a>). Wengi, akiwemo mchawi maarufu aitwaye Simoni, walibatizwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:9-Acts8:13\">Matendo 8:9–13</a>).</p><p>Malaika alimwongoza Filipo kusafiri kuelekea kusini magharibi kutoka Yerusalemu kwenda Gaza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">Matendo 8:26</a>). Huko, Roho alimwelekeza kukutana na mweka hazina wa Wakushi, ambaye alikuwa akirudi nyumbani kutoka Yerusalemu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:27-Acts8:28\">Matendo 8:27–28</a>). Mwethiopia alimwomba Filipo aeleze <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:1-Isa53:12\">Isaya 53</a>. Filipo alishiriki ujumbe kuhusu Yesu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:30-Acts8:35\">Matendo 8:30–35</a>) na kumbatiza mtu kando ya barabara (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:36-Acts8:38\">8:36–38</a>). Roho wa Mungu kisha alimchukua Filipo ghafla hadi Azota (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:39-Acts8:40\">Matendo 8:39–40</a>). Alilihubiri ujumbe huko na kusafiri kupitia miji ya pwani hadi kufika Kaisaria, mji mkubwa wa Kirumi, ambapo huenda alikaa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:40\">Matendo 8:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:8-Acts21:9\">21:8–9</a>).</p><p>Miaka mingi baadaye, Paulo alilala usiku kucha nyumbani kwa Filipo huko Kaisaria (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:8\">Matendo 21:8</a>). Kufikia wakati huo, watu walimfahamu Filipo kama Filipo Mwinjilisti. Alikuwa na binti wanne ambao hawajaolewa, na wote walikuwa na kipawa cha unabii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:9\">Matendo 21:9</a>).</p><p>Filipo anawakilisha wahubiri wa Kikristo wa mwanzo. Roho Mtakatifu aliwapa nguvu na kuwaongoza kuthibitisha ujumbe wao (tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">Matendo 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:4-Acts3:8\">3:4–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:12-Acts5:16\">5:12–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8\">6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:9-Acts10:20\">10:9–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6-Acts16:10\">16:6–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:11-Acts19:12\">19:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:22-Acts20:23\">20:22–23</a>). Filipo alifuata nguvu na mwongozo wa Roho, na Mungu alimtumia kueneza Habari Njema zaidi ya Yudea.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:5\">Matendo 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4-Acts8:13\">8:4–13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26-Acts8:40\">26–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:8-Acts21:9\">21:8–9</a></p>",
